# React Native performance

When editing matched files for **React Native or Expo** performance work:

1. Open [`skills/react-native-best-practices/SKILL.md`](https://github.com/callstackincubator/agent-skills/blob/main/skills/react-native-best-practices/SKILL.md) (or the local file if this repo is in the workspace) for problem → reference routing.
2. **Profile before** suggesting memoization hooks or micro-optimizations.
3. Prefer concrete references under `skills/react-native-best-practices/references/` (lists, bundle, native, JS) over generic advice.

If `skills/` is not in the workspace, tell the user to add this repository’s `skills/` content per the upstream README.
